data.description: Seaside Bliss with a Lucrative Twist! Welcome to your dream 2 bed, 2 bath, 1151 sq ft condo in Miramar Beach! This Gulf-front gem not only offers breathtaking views but also serves as a savvy investment with a rental income exceeding $43,000 annually. Luxuriate in style with a recent 2-year renovation, and indulge in the myriad of upscale amenities including a restaurant, private tiki bar, heated and cooled corridors, swimming deck, day spa, gym, tennis courts, sauna, covered parking, and an owner's garage. Priced affordably and featuring not just one, but two income-producing units within its walls, this property is a savvy investor's dream. BACK ON MARKET DUE TO NO FAULT OF THE SELLERS.
